	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64968827"><p>Quick question for everyone: If you're D.B. Cooper and you're smart enough go pull off the most amazing air piracy in history, with legions of FBI and amateur sleuths looking for you...</p><p>Why would you keep the parachute around?</p><p>Why not just burn it some summer evening, cut it up into strips and throw it away piecemeal, or bury it?</p><p>Why even keep the skydiving log?</p><p>While there's significant emotional appeal to going public and showing off how smart you are, I think he would also recognize that doing that would make the rest of his life miserable.</p></div>
	</div>

